summary: My first mod. It's a simple re-texture of the base brown Thieves Guild Armor for all parts of both male and female.
descriptionHtml: My first mod. It's a simple re-texture of the base brown Thieves Guild Armor for all parts of both male and female. I plan on updating with the others when I get more time. [u][b]WARNING:[/b][/u] DOES NOT support custom body mods. So far no bugs have been found after running in vanilla and heavily modded, if any are found please let me know.
author: cwjbeast57
